          "canonical": "[ edit | edit source ]\n • Thorn Tooth can be harvested in the Deepmines Nutrient Plant of Weed The Garden Deepmines Bounty .\n • May be awarded randomly as a bonus bounty reward at the end of the mission, appearing just beside the extraction elevator.\n\n• Can be purchased for 10 Fergolyte from Nightcap at Rank 0 - Neutral .\n\n | Location\n |\n | Mushroom |\n | Effect\n |\n\n | Deepmines Nutrient Plant\n(Stage 2-5 zone in Weed The Garden bounty)\n |\n | Blister Stalk\n |\n | Weapons inflict Heat Damage. Spawns six false Syzygy Shockwave MOAs that surround and follow the player while dancing in place.\n |\n\n | Thorn Tooth\n |\n | Weapons inflict Puncture Damage. Both the player and any enemies they damage will be impaled with ethereal Skana s.\n |\n\n | Gamma Berry\n |\n | Weapons inflict Radiation Damage. The player's head temporarily inflates.\n |\n\n | Nonono\n |\n | Weapons inflict Void Damage. Player is surrounded by Void energy, audible laughter plays on pickup, and the buff description reads \"Is someone watching?\"\n |",
